<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%= render 'header' %>

<body id="page-top">

  <!-- Navigation Bar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-secondary text-uppercase fixed-top" id="mainNav">
    <div class="container">
      <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item active"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right text-uppercase font-weight-bold bg-primary text-white rounded" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
        Menu
        <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
      </button>
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
        <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
          <li class="nav-item mx-0 mx-lg-1">
            <a class="nav-link py-3 px-0 px-lg-3 rounded js-scroll-trigger" href="#section2">Our Resellers</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item mx-0 mx-lg-1">
            <a class="nav-link py-3 px-0 px-lg-3 rounded js-scroll-trigger" href="#section3">Become a Reseller</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item mx-0 mx-lg-1">
            <a class="nav-link py-3 px-0 px-lg-3 rounded js-scroll-trigger" href="products.html">Products</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Masthead -->
  <header class="masthead text-white text-center">
    <div class="container d-flex align-items-center flex-column">

      <!-- Masthead Heading -->
      <h1 class="masthead-heading text-uppercase mb-0 text-primary">Monk Makes Ltd</h1>

      <!-- Masthead Subheading -->
      <p class="masthead-subheading font-weight-light mb-0 text-primary">Manufacturer of kits and accessories for the BBC micro:bit and Raspberry Pi.</p>
      <br/>
      <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B-Kwyqk37fgpM0Jtd29fUlFCQ2s"  height="400" alt="...">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?id=0B-Kwyqk37fgpN1lDSE1zMzc2Y0k" height="400" alt="...">
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="font-weight-light mb-0 text-primary text-left">
        <br/>
        <p>Founded in 2013, Monk Makes Ltd designs and manufacturers 
          a wide range of electronics kits and circuit boards from its base in the North West of England.</p>
        <p>Nearly all of our products are manufacturerd or assembled 
            in the UK using our PCB assembly facility and our local workforce.</p>
        <p>As well as supporting educators, our products are also popular
          with electronics makers and enthusiasts.</p>
        <p>We are not a retail outlet, we concentrate on out strength 
          in design and manufacturing and so, if you have come here looking to 
          buy a specific product, then please click <a href="#">HERE</a> to find a product information for each of our products. 
          Each product page has direct links to the BUY page from our retailers who stock that product.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Retailers Section -->
  <section class="page-section portfolio bg-primary text-white" id="section2">
    <div class="container align-items-center flex-column">

      <!-- Retailers Heading -->
      <h1 class="page-section-heading text-center text-uppercase mb-0">Our Resellers</h1>
      <p class="masthead-subheading font-weight-light mb-0">Here is our current list of distributers. Click on the button to see the 
        MonkMakes products that they sell.</p>
      
      <br/>

      <!-- Grid Items -->
      <div class="row text-primary">

<%
country = ''
retailers = Retailer.all
retailers = retailers.sort_by{|a| [a.delivery_ad_country, -a.shipments.length]}
retailers.each do | retailer |
    if (not retailer.is_retail and retailer.active and retailer.include_in_website)
        country = retailer.billing_ad_country
%>
        <!-- Retailer Info -->
        <div class="card" style="width: 15rem; height: 15rem; spacing: 10">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="<%=retailer.logo_url%>" alt="<%=retailer.name%>">
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <div class="mt-auto">
                <a href="" class="btn btn-primary">Web Store</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <img src="img/flags/<%=country.downcase%>-64.png" alt="<%=country%>"/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

<%          
        end 
    end %>

      </div>
      <!-- /.row -->

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section: Become a Reseller -->
  <section class="page-section mb-0" id="section3">
    <div class="container d-flex align-items-center flex-column">

      <!-- Become a Retailer Section Heading -->
      <h1 class="page-section-heading text-center text-uppercase text-primary">Become a Reseller</h1>

      <!-- Become a Retailer Content -->
      <div class="row">
        <div>
          <br/>
          <p>If you would like to become a reseller of MonkMakes products, then
            please email linda@monkmakes.com. She'll need a few details from you 
            and then you can start ordering at our wholesale prices.
          </p> 
          <p>We are a small company and like to keep things agile. We ship orders 
            often on the day or order and won't tie you up with contracts.
          </p>
          <p>We are happy to support new businessses around the world who are 
            making the most of these exciting times as micro:bit rolls out around
            the globe.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <%= render 'footer' %>

</body>

</html>
